  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Dragon's a cosy hotel with a great atmosphere and breath-taking views. The hotel rooms have been renovated to a fantastic standard with modern features and alpine charm. The hotel's just 100 metres from the centre, putting you in the perfect location for exploring the local area.</p>
<h2>A buzzing atmosphere and fantastic wine bar</h2>
<p>The hotel has a fantastic bar, making it a popular spot in town. There's a small sun terrace where you can sit and relax with an aperitivo, it's great for catching some summer sun and admiring the dramatic mountains surrounding the hotel. For something a bit more unique you can arrange a wine tasting (payable locally) in the hotel bar. The bar stocks over 200 wine labels and it's been decorated in a cosy and intimate alpine-style.</p>
<h2>Great access to local walking trails</h2>
<p>You're just 150 metres from the Cretaz lift which which makes getting to know the mountains on foot or by bike really easy. With Cervinia's high altitude there are lots of hiking trails to discover in the area. Grab your walking boots and head out to explore wonderful scenery.</p>]]></description>
